item.title: Maternity Fashion game
item.description: In this exciting game you have to take care of the appearance of a pregnant girl. Choose the appropriate clothes in which the heroine of the game will look most impressive. You will also need to take care of shoes and accessories. Do not forget about a cute hairstyle, it is also an important element of the image.
